# <type>(<scope>): <subject>
#
# type: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, perf, test, chore, ci, security
# scope: api, web, docker, github, crypto, storage, database, etc.
# subject: brief description in present tense (lowercase, no period)
#
# Examples:
# feat(api): add file sharing between users
# fix(docker): upgrade npm to resolve CVE-2025-64756
# docs(readme): update installation instructions
# chore(deps): upgrade drizzle-orm to v0.45.1
# security(deps): patch validator vulnerability
#
# Body (optional): Explain what and why, not how
# - Detail 1
# - Detail 2
#
# Footer (optional): Breaking changes, issue references
# BREAKING CHANGE: describe what breaks
# Fixes #123
# Closes #456

